Warren Casey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Warren_Casey 0 Warren Casey (April 20, 1935 – November 8, 1988) was an American theatre composer, lyricist, writer, and actor. He was the writer and composer, with Jim Jacobs, of the stage musical Grease. Warren_Casey ( April_20_,_1935 – November_8_,_1988 ) was an_American_theatre_composer , lyricist , writer , and actor .
